If I chose my tracking platefrom Clickbank directly to promote clickbank offer then What should be my landing page URL should be on news breack

If you're using ClickBank as your tracking platform to promote a ClickBank offer on NewsBreak, your landing page URL should include the `__CALLBACK_PARAM__` macro. This is important for tracking purposes. Here's an example of how your ClickBank tracking URL might look:

`https://hop.clickbank.net/?vendor=[seller_account_nickname]&affiliate=[affiliate_account_nickname]&lid=6100&tid=__CALLBACK_PARAM__`

Make sure to replace `[seller_account_nickname]` and `[affiliate_account_nickname]` with your actual account nicknames.

For more detailed instructions, you can refer to our guide on setting up a ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak: [How to set up a ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/23746617571341-How-to-set-up-a-ClickBank-Postback-on-NewsBreak)
